        "authorId" : "4a3ee9f8-9e7c-459e-b715-28669578f2c0",
        "body" : "@jakirkham - I thought this was something we got with conda-build 3 and the conda-forge-pinnings",
        "createdAt" : "2018-04-25T18:49:07Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2018-04-25T18:49:07Z",
